  "question": "Which of the following statements(s) is/are true concerning human\nenergy requirement?",
  "options": {
    "A": "In normal subjects, less than 5% of basal energy requirement is spent\non cardiac output and the work of breathing",
    "B": "Mechanical ventilation can decrease the energy expenditure"
  },
  "answer": "UNKNOWN) ",
